title: American Horror Story Weekly Wednesday Live Stream
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: I really hope our location for this season is a summer camp. It’s something we’ve always wanted

Of course I love The Shining, The Thing, Aliens, A Nightmare on Elm St., Howling, Scanners, The Fly, American Werewolf in London, BUT... Creepshow, Night of the Creeps, Motel Hell, The Night of the Living Dead, Fright Night, Trick or Treat, Night of the Comet (mild horror) & The Midnight Hour are some of my favorite 80’s Horror films (maybe I like camp, lol.)
It's crazy that it's already May and we don't have any plot hints or more casting news. Just only Emma & Gus.
When my husband goes out of town for work I used to play Carole King and mope in a fluffy robe the whole time (not Metal.)
